* Can probably go a ways yet within the unit test environment
  StorageNode to aggregate CRL, Stores, Per-store TxManagers, and network interface implementers
  AspenSystem to implement client interface (constructor takes a UUID for client identifier, default to random)
  InProc Network
    - Could go ZMQ and use inproc
